<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/CL_0000068> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "duct epithelial cell" .
<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/CL_0000068> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#seeAlso> "https://cellxgene.cziscience.com/cellguide/CL_0000068" .
