<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/CL_0001035> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> "A connective tissue cell found in bone." .
<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/CL_0001035> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/RO_0002175> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/NCBITaxon_9606> .
