_:B048480b0e3677fe259428325b08a9210 <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#annotatedTarget> "The pituitary gland is an endocrine gland that secretes hormones that regulate many other glands [GO]. An endocrine gland located ventral to the diencephalon and derived from mixed neuroectodermal and non neuroectodermal origin [ZFIN]." .
_:B048480b0e3677fe259428325b08a9210 <http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#hasDbXref> "Wikipedia:Pituitary_gland" .
