_:B1edc6c5d8c133aa6b5186079edb16d2e <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#annotatedTarget> "An endocrine gland derived from infundibulum of the floor of the diencephalon and an ectodermal dorsal protrusion from the buccal cavity which controls the secretion of many hormones influencing the function of various organs of the body.[AAO]" .
