_:Be5537cf5da2e9275dd58d2b7859c7f43 <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#annotatedTarget> "Either of a pair of glandular pouches that lie one on either side of the male reproductive tract posterolateral to the urinary bladder and in the human male secrete a sugar- and protein-containing fluid into the ejaculatory duct." .
